description: This beautiful truck is bringing the luau vibes to Buffalo with its scene of a Hawaiian sunset that’s as serene as it’s delicious cuisine. Their menu features classic Hawaiian favorites, including Hawaiian BBQ Chicken, Chicken Katsu, and BBQ Short Ribs. Don’t forget that they’re doling out sides of white rice, Hawaiian Macaroni Salad, and a wedge of juicy pineapple with every plate. Make sure to come out to say “Aloha!” because we’re not lyin’ about the quality of this tasty Hawaiian BBQ.
name: Hawaiian BBQ
